**Full citation:** Z. Grujiƒá, "Localization and geometric depletion of vortex-stretching in the 3D NSE," *Communications in Mathematical Physics*, 290, 861‚Äì870 (2009).

**Main theorem (paraphrased):** The vortex-stretching term admits spatiotemporal localization to an arbitrarily small parabolic cylinder Q = B(x‚ÇÄ,r) √ó (t‚ÇÄ ‚àí r¬≤, t‚ÇÄ). Under a *local* version of the ¬Ω-H√∂lder coherence condition on Œæ within Q, regularity follows at (x‚ÇÄ, t‚ÇÄ), independently of global behavior.

