**Citation:** A. Cheskidov and R. Shvydkoy, "The regularity of weak solutions of the 3D Navier-Stokes equations in B^{-1}_{‚àû,‚àû}," *Archive for Rational Mechanics and Analysis* 195(1): 159‚Äì169, 2010. arXiv:0708.3067.

