+
+```text
+X_{1,n} -> X_{2,n} -> X_{3,n} -> X_{4,n} -> X_{1,n+1}
+```
+
+and decide which candidate differences are:
+
+- `cosmetic`
+- `potentially load-bearing`
+- `already closed`
+
