+# Final Report: Strategy 001
+
+## Executive Verdict
+
+```text
+mechanism-level negative: Tao's cascade can be reconstructed sharply, but no candidate firewall survives as a concrete exact-NS object
+```
+
+- [VERIFIED] Phase 0 succeeded: Tao's averaged-NS blowup is a five-mode delayed-threshold circuit embedded into a shell cascade, not a vague high-frequency cascade slogan.
+- [VERIFIED] Phase 1 succeeded: the intervention map reduced the live discrepancy to one candidate family, namely exact-NS circuit non-isolability.
+- [CHECKED] That candidate family splits into:
+  - triadic coefficient rigidity,
+  - unavoidable spectator couplings,
+  - exact Leray-projection rigidity as the mechanism enforcing the first two.
+- [CHECKED] Strategy verdict: this is the best mechanism-level story, but it still does **not** survive as a concrete firewall object. It remains a qualitative statement that exact NS interactions are too entangled to realize Tao's engineered circuit, not a sharp inequality, flux law, incompatibility theorem, or dynamical constraint ready for proof use.
+
+## Directions Tried
+
+### 1. Phase 0 Mechanism Reconstruction
+
+- [VERIFIED] Exploration 001 reconstructed Tao's mechanism at three distinct layers:
+  - averaged operator,
+  - five-mode circuit `(a,b,c,d,\u00e3)`,
+  - shell blowup induction with variables `X_{1,n}, X_{2,n}, X_{3,n}, X_{4,n}, X_{1,n+1}`.
+- [VERIFIED] The load-bearing mechanism is delayed threshold activation:
+  - a weak pump grows `X_{2,n}`,
+  - an exponentially tiny seed `X_{3,n}` is amplified,
+  - a rotor rapidly exchanges energy between `X_{1,n}` and `X_{4,n}`,
+  - a final pump transfers energy to `X_{1,n+1}`,
+  - shell-to-shell times shrink summably.
+- [VERIFIED] This gave the exact mechanism steps needed for later comparison against real NS.
+
+### 2. Phase 1 Real-NS Intervention Map
+
+- [VERIFIED] Exploration 002 compared Tao's literal chain
+
+```text
+X_{1,n} -> X_{2,n} -> X_{3,n} -> X_{4,n} -> X_{1,n+1}
+```
+
+  against the exact Fourier/Leray NS interaction law
+
+```text
+‚àÇt √ª(k) + |k|^2 √ª(k)
+  = -i ‚àë_{p+q=k} (q¬∑√ª(p)) P_k √ª(q).
+```
+
+- [VERIFIED] The following candidate routes were closed again at the mechanism level:
+  - frame-shift / Galilean pressure gain,
+  - harmonic far-field pressure as a standalone route,
+  - LP / Bernstein cleanup,
+  - commutator / CLMS reformulation,
+  - generic div-free level-set improvement,
+  - near-Beltrami / exact-symmetry generalization.
+- [CHECKED] The only surviving candidate family was exact-NS circuit non-isolability:
+  - Tao engineers five effective couplings with distinct scales and signs,
+  - exact NS uses one rigid quadratic law plus full triad summation and exact projection,
+  - once a desired triad is activated, additional same-scale, cross-scale, conjugate, and projected couplings appear automatically.
+
+## Strongest Findings
+
+1. [VERIFIED] Tao's blowup depends on an unusually isolated circuit, not merely on having forward energy transfer.
+2. [VERIFIED] The decisive Tao variable is the tiny trigger `X_{3,n}`, whose role is dynamically central but energetically negligible until threshold crossing.
+3. [CHECKED] The sharpest exact-NS mismatch is therefore not "pressure is nonlocal" in the abstract, but "exact NS seems to force interaction entanglement where Tao needs near-isolated gate logic."
+4. [CHECKED] That mismatch is real as a mechanism-level insight, but still too vague as a firewall candidate: it has not been sharpened into a concrete object of the kind the strategy required.
+
+## Negative Results and Dead Ends
+
+- [VERIFIED] Harmonic far-field pressure does not survive as the right obstruction object; `P_{k1}` is already favorable and the bad term is local `P_{k21}`.
+- [VERIFIED] Pressure/frame tricks are closed by Galilean invariance of the pressure source.
+- [VERIFIED] LP/paraproduct and commutator routes are already closed structurally in predecessor work and do not re-open here.
+- [VERIFIED] Beltrami-type exact cancellation is real but measure-zero; predecessor work already shows it collapses under perturbation and does not yield a generic firewall.
+- [CHECKED] The surviving "circuit non-isolability" story fails the Phase 2 bar because it does not yet specify:
+  - a quantitative notion of "almost closed five-mode subsystem",
+  - a sharp exact-NS impossibility statement,
+  - a usable inequality or dynamical invariant that a proof framework could target.
+
+## Strongest Candidate and Why It Failed
+
+### Candidate
+
+- [CHECKED] `Exact-NS circuit non-isolability`: the exact quadratic/Leray interaction structure does not permit an almost closed five-mode subsystem with Tao's pump/amplifier/rotor hierarchy.
+
+### Why It Was The Best Candidate
+
+- [VERIFIED] It was tied directly to Tao's actual mechanism.
+- [CHECKED] It did not collapse into an already-closed estimate route.
+- [CHECKED] It naturally bundled triadic rigidity, spectator leakage, and exact projection effects.
+
+### Why It Still Fails
+
+- [CHECKED] It remains a mechanism description, not a concrete firewall object.
+- [CHECKED] In its current form it is too close to the slogan:
+
+```text
+exact NS has too much interaction entanglement
+```
+
+  which is directionally plausible but not yet mathematically actionable.
+- [CHECKED] The natural host framework would be an exact Fourier/helical triad geometry or "no near-closed circuit" theorem, but the candidate has not been sharpened enough to support such a program within this strategy.
+
+## Recommended Next Move for the Missionary
+
+- [CHECKED] Treat this strategy as a negative but useful ground-clearing result.
+- [CHECKED] Carry forward two things only:
+  - Tao's mechanism reconstruction,
+  - the focused hypothesis that any real firewall would have to look like an exact-NS no-circuit / non-isolability statement, not an estimate improvement.
+- [CHECKED] Only spend more budget here if willing to launch a very specific follow-up mission:
+
+```text
+formalize and test an exact Fourier/helical "no near-closed Tao circuit" theorem
+```
+
+  with a precise quantitative notion of admissible couplings and spectator leakage.
+- [CHECKED] Otherwise mark the lead closed for now. On current evidence it is a mechanism-level curiosity, not a usable firewall.
+
+## Claims Worth Carrying Forward
+
+- [VERIFIED] Tao's averaged blowup is a five-mode delayed-threshold circuit embedded into a shell cascade.
+- [VERIFIED] The tiny trigger variable is mechanism-central.
+- [CHECKED] The best remaining exact-NS contrast is circuit isolation versus exact interaction entanglement.
+- [CHECKED] No concrete firewall object emerged from that contrast within this strategy.
